[
  {
    "content_id": 796785,
    "reference_id": 12170,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>信息</span>（或<em>神諭</em>；和合本譯為：默示）這個詞表明這卷書是神藉著祂的先知所啟示的話（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:1\">鴻1:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:1\">瑪1:1</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:1",
          "end_ref": "35001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796787,
    "reference_id": 12172,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>呼求......不應允</span>.....？聖經中呼求或應允的主題，通常表明了說話者信靠神作為避難所和引導者（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:1-Ps102:2\">詩102:1–2</a>），並顯示信徒與神之間親密的相交（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:18\">詩145:18</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:24\">賽65:24</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:2",
          "end_ref": "35001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796786,
    "reference_id": 12171,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:2–4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001002-35001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在哈巴谷看來，神似乎對猶大境內充斥的罪惡無動於衷（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:3-Hab1:4\">1:3–4</a>），亦對他為此所發的訴求也毫無回應（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:2\">1:2</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:2",
          "end_ref": "35001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796788,
    "reference_id": 12173,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在哈巴谷的時代，毀滅和強暴充斥著猶大的社會（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"HabIntro_BookIntro_Filament\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">哈巴谷書簡介</span>，「背景」）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:3",
          "end_ref": "35001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796789,
    "reference_id": 12174,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>哈巴谷對周遭充斥的不公與不義深感憂慮（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:12-Hab1:13\">1:12–13</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:4\">2:4</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:9\">9</a>），即使在法庭之中，律法也已失去維持公義的效力。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:4",
          "end_ref": "35001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796791,
    "reference_id": 12176,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>看......看（和合本譯為：<span>觀看</span>）：這裡的兩個希伯來文動詞都譯為<em>看</em>（<em>look</em>），在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:3\">一章3節</a>中則分別譯為<span>看見</span>（see）和<em>看着</em>（<em>watch</em>）。這形成了一個文學上的呼應，將哈巴谷在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:3\">一章3節</a>的提問與神在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:5-Hab1:11\">一章5至11節</a>的回應連結起來。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:5",
          "end_ref": "35001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796790,
    "reference_id": 12175,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:5–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001005-35001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神對哈巴谷的問題的回應出人意料。祂要差遣一個殘暴的民族——巴比倫人——來對付猶大的強暴。這支巴比倫軍隊訓練有素、久經沙場，是勢不可擋的力量。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:5",
          "end_ref": "35001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796792,
    "reference_id": 12177,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>任意而行（和合本譯為：<span>都任意發出</span>）：巴比倫人不會帶來任何公義的伸張。他們自立法則，而這更讓先知困惑，神為何用他們來懲治猶大的決定。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:7",
          "end_ref": "35001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796793,
    "reference_id": 12178,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>豹、<span>豺狼</span>和鷹的鮮明形象，刻畫出巴比倫人攻擊猶大時的速度、兇猛和掠食的本性（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:13\">耶4:13</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:40\">48:40</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:22\">49:22</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:8",
          "end_ref": "35001008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796794,
    "reference_id": 12179,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>巴比倫人確實在公元前605年至586年間，將許多猶大人擄到異地（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:1-Dan1:3\">但1:1–3</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:9",
          "end_ref": "35001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796779,
    "reference_id": 12164,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在古代近東地區，攻城時用土築成斜坡以攻向受圍城市的城牆，這種戰術有被廣泛地記載（例，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:32\">王下19:32</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:1\">鴻2:1</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:10",
          "end_ref": "35001010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796780,
    "reference_id": 12165,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>以自己的勢力為神</span>：巴比倫人崇拜許多假神。他們對自己軍事力量的傲慢自信，就好像其為偶像之一。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:11",
          "end_ref": "35001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796782,
    "reference_id": 12167,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>儘管心中困惑，哈巴谷並沒有否認神。他以我的神、我的聖者的語言來重申自己對耶和華的委身，然後才提出對神向他所啟示之事的嚴肅疑問。</p></li><li><p>基於神的屬性和祂與以色列所立的約關係，哈巴谷確信神不會將祂的子民完全滅絕。</p></li><li><p>&nbsp;為了糾正我們（和合本譯為：<span>為要刑罰人</span>）：參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5-Heb12:11\">希伯來書十二章5至11\b節</a>。</p></li><li><p>我們的磐石（和合本譯為：<span>磐石啊</span>）：這是常用來形容神信實與能力的形象（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:15\">申32:15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:2\">撒上2:2</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2\">詩18:2</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:4\">林前10:4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:6-1Pet2:8\">彼前2:6–8</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:12",
          "end_ref": "35001012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796781,
    "reference_id": 12166,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:12–2:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001012-35002001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>哈巴谷很難將神的回應（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:5-Hab1:11\">1:5–11</a>）與他對神屬性的認識調和起來。聖潔公義的神怎能用比猶大更不義的民族來管教猶大呢？</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:12",
          "end_ref": "35002001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796783,
    "reference_id": 12168,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:14–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001014-35001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>魚……<span>鈎</span>……網：哈巴谷將巴比倫人比喻為漁夫，將被征服的民族像魚一樣捕捉上來。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:14",
          "end_ref": "35001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796784,
    "reference_id": 12169,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 1:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35001016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"12165\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">一章11節的研讀註釋</span>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:21\">約翰<span>一書五章</a>21節</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35001016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:16",
          "end_ref": "35001016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 1:16"
        }
      ],
