  {
    "content_id": 796798,
    "reference_id": 12183,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>我......立在望樓上</span>：哈巴谷像一名在望樓上的守望者一樣（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:24-2Sam18:28\">撒下18:24–28</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:17-2Kgs9:20\">王下9:17–20</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:2-Ezek33:6\">結33:2–6</a>）耐心等候，盼望看見神如何回應他的申訴，即使這意味著要接受耶和華的責備。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:1",
          "end_ref": "35002001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796802,
    "reference_id": 12187,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神吩咐先知把這信息（字面意思是<em>異象</em>；和合本譯為：<span>默示</span>）清楚地寫下來，好使人能明白、保存，並傳給別人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:2",
          "end_ref": "35002002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796800,
    "reference_id": 12185,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:2–5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002002-35002005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>哈巴谷的使命是要清楚地告訴百姓，即使神的公義看似延遲，祂的審判終必臨到。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:2",
          "end_ref": "35002005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796799,
    "reference_id": 12184,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:2–20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002002-35002020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神回應了哈巴谷的第二個申訴（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:12-Hab2:1\">1:12–2:1</a>），但並沒有解釋祂為何揀選巴比倫人。相反，祂保證一切強暴和不義都必受懲罰。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:2",
          "end_ref": "35002020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796803,
    "reference_id": 12188,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>必然臨到</span>：在唯有耶和華知道的特定日期，祂要介入人類歷史，使其按著祂的計畫走向適當的終局，為義人伸冤，並審判惡人。神的子民必須耐心等候，因為神的計畫正如期進行（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:35-Heb10:38\">來10:35–38</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:3",
          "end_ref": "35002003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796804,
    "reference_id": 12189,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>神知道驕傲之人以自我為中心，他們彎曲的行為顯明自己的不義；他們拒絕神的教訓，滿足自己的私慾（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:15\">箴12:15</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:8\">21:8</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:29\">29</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:27\">29:27</a>）。與此相反，義人在神面前享有正當的司法地位，他們以神的公義標準為自己的準則，並在生活中實踐出來。</p></li><li><p><span>信（</span>faithfulness<span>）</span>：希伯來文為 ’emunah。在創世記中，這個詞的詞根（’mn）是用來形容亞伯蘭信靠神（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:6\">創15:6</a>）。神改變那些信靠祂之人的心，使他們能忠心遵行神的聖潔標準。另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:16-Rom1:17\">羅馬書一章16至17節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:11\">加拉太書三章11節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:37-Heb10:39\">希伯來書十章37至39節</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:4",
          "end_ref": "35002004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796806,
    "reference_id": 12191,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:6–8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002006-35002008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>在哈巴谷的第一首諷刺詩中，他譴責巴比倫人劫掠列國。</p></li><li><p>搶奪……勒索（<span>和合本譯為：增添不屬自己的財</span>物......<span>多多取人的當頭</span>）：這個意象將巴比倫人比喻為債主，他們以壓迫性的手段使債務人起來反抗他們。貪婪很容易玷污個人或一個民族的屬靈品格（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15\">路12:15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3\">弗5:3</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
