  {
    "content_id": 796805,
    "reference_id": 12190,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:6–20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002006-35002020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>五首諷刺詩（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:6-Hab2:8\">2:6–8</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:9-Hab2:11\">9–11</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:12-Hab2:14\">12–14</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:15-Hab2:17\">15–17</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:18-Hab2:20\">18–20</a>）是在描繪神將來對巴比倫人（以及一切像巴比倫人一樣沉溺於強暴和不義之人）的審判。神任憑他們自取滅亡。當惡人受審判時，那些曾受苦的人將能重複這些諷刺的話（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:14-Hab1:17\">1:14–17</a>）。每一首諷刺詩都包含一個哀嘆、一個審判，以及神施行審判的理由。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:6",
          "end_ref": "35002020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796807,
    "reference_id": 12192,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:9–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002009-35002011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在第二首諷刺詩中，巴比倫人因其詭詐的行徑而受到譴責。巴比倫人藉著欺詐與不誠實得來建造大房子的資源，因此斷送了自己的性命。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:9",
          "end_ref": "35002011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796795,
    "reference_id": 12180,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:12–14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002012-35002014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>在第三首諷刺詩中，巴比倫人因其奪取人命、敗壞社會的行為而受譴責，他們藉此獲得財富來建造自己的城邑。神要使他們看似的得益完全化為損失。</p></li><li><p><span>充滿遍地</span>：與強暴和不義之財相對的是對耶和華榮耀的<span>知識</span>，神應許這<span>知識</span>要像水充滿<span>洋海</span>一樣普及（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:9\">賽11:9</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:12",
          "end_ref": "35002014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796796,
    "reference_id": 12181,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:15–17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002015-35002017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在第四首諷刺詩中，巴比倫人因他們加諸於人、動物與環境的可恥行徑而受譴責。他們就像一個看似好客的人，卻在使鄰舍喝醉之後，剝奪他們的一切。然而，巴比倫人將在喝下耶和華審判之杯後蒙羞（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:15-Jer25:17\">耶25:15–17</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:11\">約18:11</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:15",
          "end_ref": "35002017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796797,
    "reference_id": 12182,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:18–20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002018-35002020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在第五首諷刺詩中，巴比倫人因他們對偶像的虔誠而受譴責。無論偶像是人手雕刻的還是鑄造的，都不能拯救人，也不能教導敬拜它們的人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:17\">賽42:17</a>）。唯有耶和華配得我們的敬拜（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:20\">哈2:20</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:2-Exod20:6\">出20:2–6</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:1-Eccl5:2\">傳5:1–2</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:18",
          "end_ref": "35002020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796801,
    "reference_id": 12186,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 2:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35002020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這一系列諷刺詩以一個宣告作結：掌管萬國的，並不是巴比倫的偶像（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:18-Hab2:20\">2:18–20</a>），而是那位聖潔的神。與毫無生命的巴比倫偶像不同，又真又活的神住在祂的聖殿中。祂的同在充滿了天上的聖所（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:1-Isa6:5\">賽6:1–5</a>）——在哈巴谷的時代，也充滿了耶路撒冷的聖殿（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:10-1Kgs8:11\">王上8:10–11</a>）。神掌管全地，並期望世人以謙卑順服的心敬拜祂（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1-Ps63:4\">詩63:1–4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:1-Jer10:10\">耶10:1–10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:16\">彌7:16</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:13\">亞2:13</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35002020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:20",
          "end_ref": "35002020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 2:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796808,
    "reference_id": 12193,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 3:1–19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35003001-35003019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>哈巴谷的預言以一首詩篇式的禱告作結。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 3:1",
          "end_ref": "35003019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 3:19"
        }
      ],
