    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796823,
    "reference_id": 12208,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 3:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>擊打江河……分開洋海（和合本譯為：<span>向江河發怒氣、向洋海發憤恨</span>）：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:19-Exod7:20\">出埃及記七章19至20節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:15-Exod14:31\">十四章15至31節</a>。</p></li><li><p>救恩的戰車（和合本譯為：<span>得勝的車</span>）：這是對埃及戰車反諷的回聲——當神帶領以色列人經紅海逃脫時，埃及的戰車曾追趕他們（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:9\">出14:9</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35003008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 3:8",
          "end_ref": "35003008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 3:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 796822,
    "reference_id": 12207,
    "title": "哈巴谷書 3:8–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "35003008-35003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶和華是為祂子民爭戰的神聖戰士，為他們施行救贖的大能。神作為戰士的主題貫穿舊約聖經與新約聖經：在舊約聖經中，這可見於在以色列人出埃及、前往西奈山（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:1-Exod15:18\">出15:1–18</a>）、自南地進入應許之地，以及早期征服時期的勝利（例，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:4-Judg5:5\">士5:4–5</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:8-Ps18:16\">詩18:8–16</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:16-Ps77:20\">77:16–20</a>；在新約聖經中重要的例子則在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11-Rev19:21\">啟19:11–21</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "35003008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "HAB 3:8",
          "end_ref": "35003015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "HAB 3:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
